1. Drop the analysis_options.yaml file into the project root as stated in
https://medium.com/flutter-community/watch-your-code-dart-flutter-lint-55a697d01c8d

https://github.com/flutter/flutter/blob/master/analysis_options.yaml

2. Before creating a plugin, check https://pub.dev/ to see if it already exists.
Follow the rules stated in the package description in order to allow it to be
used in the project.  
